N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 12 ยง 327.13 - Filing of notices

State Regulations

All notices required to be filed with the chair, pursuant
to this Part, shall be deemed filed when received at the address specified on
such forms as may be prescribed by the chair pursuant to this

Part. Notes
